      <title>西班牙试图取缔分离主义者：现在由他们做主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/basque-elections-may-see-upset-by-eta-linked-party-bildu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府释放了因与巴斯克恐怖组织“埃塔”有联系而入狱的活动人士后，大多数人就消失在了幕后。但阿纳尔多·奥特吉则不然。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/basque-elections-may-see-upset-by-eta-linked-party-bildu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克进入卢旺达移民计划最后阶段，保守党担心新的失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/rishi-sunak-enters-rwanda-migration-plan-endgame-with-uk-tories-fearing-failure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)的旗舰移民政策下周进入尾声，一些保守党人士担心这位总理让自己暴露在他所押注的首相职位问题上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/rishi-sunak-enters-rwanda-migration-plan-endgame-with-uk-tories-fearing-failure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据英国《金融时报》报道，苏纳克预计将宣布新的英国军舰计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/sunak-expected-to-announce-new-uk-warship-program-ft-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国《金融时报》援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，英国首相苏纳克正准备宣布一项新的军舰计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/sunak-expected-to-announce-new-uk-warship-program-ft-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 04:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派在令人惊讶的转折中团结在候选人周围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/venezuela-election-opposition-picks-edmundo-gonzalez-to-challenge-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派围绕即将举行的投票的暂定候选人团结起来，这种团结的表现可能对总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的连任构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/venezuela-election-opposition-picks-edmundo-gonzalez-to-challenge-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南加州大学在告别演说争议中取消毕业典礼演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/usc-cancels-commencement-speakers-amid-valedictorian-controversy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南加州大学在即将举行的毕业典礼上取消了所有外部演讲者，此前该大学取消了 2024 届毕业生致辞演讲的决定，遭到强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/usc-cancels-commencement-speakers-amid-valedictorian-controversy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中央司令部称美国空袭伊拉克的报道不属实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/centcom-says-reports-of-us-airstrikes-in-iraq-aren-t-true</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 X 上的一篇帖子称，美国中央司令部表示，有关美国今天对伊拉克进行空袭的报道并不属实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/centcom-says-reports-of-us-airstrikes-in-iraq-aren-t-true</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:28:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥总统竞选领跑者认为墨西哥国家石油公司将为其债务再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/mexico-s-frontrunner-sees-pemex-refinancing-debt-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥主要总统候选人克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 表示，她预计全球负债最重的石油生产商墨西哥国家石油公司 (Petroleo Mexicanos) 将在 2025 年债券到期之前对其债券进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/mexico-s-frontrunner-sees-pemex-refinancing-debt-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费陪审团现已定于周一在纽约进行开庭辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/trump-hush-money-jury-now-set-for-opening-arguments-in-ny-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的首次刑事审判的陪审团选拔工作于周五完成，为周一纽约一桩指控这位前总统在 2016 年大选前伪造商业记录以隐瞒性丑闻的案件的开庭辩论奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/trump-hush-money-jury-now-set-for-opening-arguments-in-ny-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:55:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行上田重申将在一段时间内保持宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/boj-s-ueda-reiterates-policy-to-remain-accommodative-for-a-while</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫重申，随着政策制定者继续购买政府债券，货币政策将在一段时间内保持宽松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/boj-s-ueda-reiterates-policy-to-remain-accommodative-for-a-while</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:34:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗与以色列的一周袭击标志着中东“游戏规则改变者”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和以色列之间长达数十年的影子战争中最激烈的一周之一周五以轻松结束，此前德黑兰宣布击败了以色列无人机对其领土的小规模袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/week-of-iran-israel-strikes-marks-a-mideast-game-changer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
